# ⚠️ IMPORTANT: Do NOT commit Cython-generated .c files!
# They contain hardcoded paths from the build machine.
# Cython will regenerate them during setup.py build_ext
# sequenzo/dissimilarity_measures/utils/*.c  # <- Should be ignored
# sequenzo/clustering/utils/*.c              # <- Should be ignored

# 通常忽略所有 .c 和 .so 文件（先写忽略规则）
*.c
*.so
*.dylib
*.o
*.a

# 再取消忽略 Pybind11 手写 C++ 源码（否定规则必须写在 *.cpp 之后才生效）
!sequenzo/dissimilarity_measures/src/*.cpp
!sequenzo/clustering/src/*.cpp
!sequenzo/clustering/sequenzo_fastcluster/src/*.cpp

# Python wheels
*.whl

# Rust build outputs
**/target/
sequenzo/rust_fast_cluster/target/

